poll4input
==========
poll files for input


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (poll4input is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install poll4input (if
necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running poll4input
------------------
Provide paths to file(s) for polling:

	poll4input file [file]...

It will exit when one of the file provides input or all files are closed
